#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:1
msgid ""
"vtkImageData/vtkRectilinearGrid/vtkStructuredGrid: Improve performance using "
"structured Points, Cells, CellTypes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:3
msgid ""
"`vtkStructuredPointArray<ValueType>` has been implemented to enable fast "
"query of structured points."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:5
msgid ""
"`vtkStructuredCellArray` has been implemented to enable fast query of "
"structured cells. `vtkStructuredCellArray` and `vtkCellArray` have "
"`vtkAbstractCellArray` as their parent class."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:8
msgid ""
"`vtkStructuredPointArray<ValueType>`, `vtkStructuredCellArray`, and "
"`vtkConstantArray<int>` are used to implement the following three functions "
"in `vtkStructuredData`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:11
msgid ""
"`vtkSmartPointer<vtkPoints> GetPoints(vtkDataArray* xCoords, vtkDataArray* "
"yCoords, vtkDataArray* zCoords, int extent[6], double dirMatrix[9])`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:13
msgid ""
"`vtkSmartPointer<vtkStructuredCellArray> GetCellArray(int extent[6], bool "
"usePixelVoxelOrientation)`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:14
msgid ""
"`vtkSmartPointer<vtkConstantArray<int>> GetCellTypesArray(int extent[6], "
"bool usePixelVoxelOrientation)`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:16
msgid ""
"The above functions are used to build the structured Points, Cells, and "
"CellTypes for `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`, and to build the "
"structured Cells, and CellTypes for `vtkStructuredGrid`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:20
msgid ""
"Using these structured classes, the performance of the following functions "
"has been optimized."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:22
msgid "`GetPoint` for `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:23
msgid ""
"`GetCellBounds` for `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`/`vtkStructuredGrid`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:24
msgid ""
"`GetCellSize` for `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`/`vtkStructuredGrid`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:25
msgid ""
"`GetCellType` for `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`/`vtkStructuredGrid`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:26
msgid ""
"`GetCellPoints` for `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`/`vtkStructuredGrid`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:27
msgid "`GetCell` for `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`/`vtkStructuredGrid`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:29
msgid ""
"`vtkImageData` and `vtkRectilinearGrid` now check for cell visibility when "
"using the `GetCell`, `GetCellSize`, and `GetCellType` functions. Also they "
"have blanking, and un-blanking capabilities of points and cells. Thanks to "
"these changes, the implementation of `vtkUniformGrid` has been greatly "
"simplified."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:33
msgid ""
"Since `vtkImageData` and `vtkRectilinearGrid` now have structured points, "
"`vtkDataSet` has a function `GetPoints` that returns the structured/explicit "
"points, if present, else it creates an internally copy of the points using "
"`GetPoint` and returns that. Thanks to this addition `void "
"vtkRectilinearGrid::GetPoints(vtkPoints* points)` has been deprecated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:37
msgid ""
"Additionally, `vtkImageData`/`vtkRectilinearGrid`/`vtkStructuredGrid` now "
"also have `GetCells` and `GetCellTypesArray` functions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:40
msgid ""
"To effectively utilize the structured Points. `vtkDataArrayRange` now has "
"`GetTuple` and `SetTuple` functions that can efficiently query the "
"structured Points when it has been dispatched."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:43
msgid ""
"To that end, the following classes/functions have been updated to "
"efficiently query the structured Points, Cells, and CellTypes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:46
msgid "`vtkTableBasedClipDataSet`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:47
msgid "`vtkStructuredDataPlaneCutter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:48
msgid "`vtkExtractGeometry`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:49
msgid "`vtkExtractCells`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:50
msgid "`vtkElevationFilter`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:51
msgid "`vtkPoints::GetPoints`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:52
msgid "`vtkBoundingBox::ComputeBounds`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:53
msgid "`vtkIOSSModel::StructuredPointsOperator`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:55
msgid ""
"Moreover, in `vtkStructuredDataPlaneCutter` when `vtkFlyingEdgesPlaneCutter` "
"is used, if scalars are not present, then a constant array is created "
"instead of using `vtkElevationFilter` for better performance. If ghosts are "
"present, and InterpolateAttributes is on then `vtkFlyingEdgesPlaneCutter` is "
"used and the ghosts are removed afterward."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-structured-points-cells-cellTypes.md:59
msgid ""
"Finally, in `vtkContourFilter`, when `vtkFlyingEdges3D` or "
"`vtkSynchronizedTemplates3D` is used, if ghosts are present. then ghosts "
"will be removed afterward."
msgstr ""
